Elizabeth Tan's Resume

Portfolio About

Hello, my name is Elizabeth.

I'm currently a generalist product designer in the civil service. We're on a mission to sustain Singapore as a leading global hub for business and investment. Previously, I cofounded a branding and inbound marketing agency, AKÃN. We put a strong focus on relational marketing and adapted human-centered methodologies for our own client. My design values have been shaped tremendously by my present and past experiences in entreprenuership, branding and business strategy. Be a Self-Starter I take ownership and initiative beyond my defined scope of responsibilities. I get things done and and seek out new learning experiences. Bring others into the design process To non-designer, no design-speak allowed. (What is design thinking even?!) Instead, invite others to experience it for themselves. Principles > Frameworks Frameworks can be rigid and ever evolving. User-centeredness will stand the test of time. Balance Trade-offs Keep a strong voice, but always consider and connect the dots across business and engineering stakeholders.
